data.description: Well cared for home with 3 bedrooms, and a room in the basementthat can be a 4th bedroom, 2 bathrooms, a big, cool Family Room, a private back yard with shed, and an oversized 2-car garage with doors and openers on both the home side, and the private dead-end alley side.  30-year warranty shingles installed 7 years ago on the roofs of the home, garage and shed.  New washer, dryer, hot water heater and humidifier.  Front stairs to be coated on 5/27.  Large jacuzzi and wall mounted TV in lower level. Extra shelving in home and garage stay.  Tons of storage.  New insulation in attic, Ejector pump 1 year old.  Home has lots of storage rooms and garage has overhead storage.
